                "NqOI0": {
                  "content": "My parallel life at the mic — seven years commentating poker for Czech Television, Czech streams of the European Poker Tour with PokerStars, and in 2026 back on Nova Sport covering tournaments from King's Casino, Rozvadov."
                },
